    <descript>
      <abstract>A trail is a linear feature constructed for the purpose of allowing the free movement of people, stock, or Off Highway Vehicles (OHV). Route measurements and route directions must correspond to those stored in the Infra Oracle table RTE_BASICS.</abstract>
      <purpose>A route system depicting all trails within or in close proximity to an administrative unit. This layer is used to depict allowed motor vehicle use management (MVUM) on the forest.</purpose>
    </descript>
